* Iron Raptor had relaxed slightly as Prowl had embraced and kissed her but when he had broken away she snarled as she finally felt the full pain of her wounded back, however, she remained verbally quiet about it as Prowl had looked over her for further wounds. But when he had exclaimed with concern about her damaged back she simply looked away and into the surrounding forest, it was no real threat to her and the bleeding had begun to clot.*

" I'm alright."

* She also had no real desire to transform into her Beast Mode, she wanted to remain in robot mode until she returned to base.
Iron Raptor then looked back at Prowl but then looked beyond him and into the distance, he might be angry that she didn't transform and begin internal repairs and she didn't have that spark at the moment to face him.*
